      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried the walking and stuff. i tried everything. it doesn't work. it's like there's no escape. you talk like you understand, but isn't there some kind of permanent fix? like a way to actually reset or just delete the parts of my brain that hurt? i need a real solution, not just \"go for a walk.\"",
